{"title":"谨防扒手　（小诗六首）","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":8,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谨防扒手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（小诗六首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇怪的偷家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝常作贼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作贼在白日。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个也平常，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有敲锣打鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂上贼的旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把空中和海上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造一个贼窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎的不叫天下诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大写讨贼歌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有自由"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你卖黄莲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不吃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你卖口香糖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也不吃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有不吃的自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你无替我吃的自由。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有不受骗的自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你无骗人的自由。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有勇士才有自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骗子永没自由。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚吧，美国侵略家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理不是你的家！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的家在哪儿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你那杀人刀下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"评艾奇逊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代的强盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盗法真是妙："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要杀人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先劝人吃迷药；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀了人，挂起刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再来一番演说。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说吧，你要叫我信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除非你死了再说。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只不过是秋蝉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然你叫嚣一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，只不过是秋蝉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风若要一吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还能叫几天？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谨防扒手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（先生们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请防扒手！）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扒手偷了你的树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树你能再植；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扒手偷了你的布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布你能再织；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若是扒手偷了你的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂不是你走错了路？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一九四九，八月某日偶成于张家口。）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}